  "title": "Senior Manager/Food Outlet Manager",
  "description": "<p>Food Outlet Manager Job Responsibilities :-</p>\n<p>* Administer purchasing and receiving procedures.</p>\n<p>* Analyse service quality and customers satisfaction.</p>\n<p>* Conduct staff performance assessment process.</p>\n<p>* Contribute to innovation process within own scope of work at the business unit.</p>\n<p>* Facilitate compliance with legislative and regulatory requirements.</p>\n<p>* Foster service innovation.</p>\n<p>* Identify and establish internal and external stakeholders relationship.</p>\n<p>* Implement loss/risk prevention.</p>\n<p>* Lead team to implement change.</p>\n<p>* Manage and implement business continuity plans.</p>\n<p>* Manage compliance with food and beverage hygiene policies and procedures.</p>\n<p>* Manage cost and quality controls.</p>\n<p>* Manage food and beverage operations.</p>\n<p>* Manage crisis situation.</p>\n<p>* Manage guest service.</p>\n<p>* Manage site/outlet and equipments maintenance.</p>\n<p>* Manage the customers dining experience.</p>\n<p>* Manage training.</p>\n<p>* Monitor income and expenses.</p>\n<p>* Optimize workforce for service excellence.</p>",
